From 4f11b71a3a47f264074961c79c5b787429ebd9f5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Juno <juno@keepliving.com>
Date: Mon, 16 Mar 2026 02:22:25 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add drag-and-drop reordering and search functionality for
 goals

Drag-and-Drop Reordering:
- Add @dnd-kit imports for drag-and-drop functionality
- Create SortableGoalCard component with visual drag handles
- Implement DndContext with PointerSensor and KeyboardSensor
- Add SortableContext with verticalListSortingStrategy
- Add DragOverlay for smooth drag preview
- Replace old HTML5 drag-and-drop with @dnd-kit
- Add 'order' field to Goal interface
- Add reorder support to PATCH /api/goals endpoint
- Goals are sorted by order field when fetching

Goal Search:
- Add search input at top of Goals section (desktop and mobile)
- Search across: title, notes, action items, source
- Real-time filtering as user types
- Clear search button (X) with results count
- Case-insensitive search
- Shows filtered count (e.g., '2/5' when searching)
- Works across both personal and collaborative goals
- Displays total matching results across all categories

Features:
- Users can grab goals by the drag handle (grip icon)
- Drag goals within the same phase to reorder
- Drag goals between phases to change status
- Type in search box to filter goals instantly
- Order persists on page refresh
